<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:2005carrot_and_turnip.PNG" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/2005carrot_and_turnip.PNG/220px-2005carrot_and_turnip.PNG" width="220" height="96" class="thumbimage" /></a>
